⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Destined Death
node ER · ER · ⟦Destined Death:ER:9b6e2f⟧

WHO   — Destined Death — the Rune of Death, removed from the Ring
WHAT  — The fated death that Marika removed from the Elden Ring at the dawn of her Order, so that true death left the world.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the Elden Ring and what was taken from it — fate, death, and the seal that holds them  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It is the element the whole plot turns on — to mend the Ring, the Tarnished must first slay death's keeper and return Death to the world.
HOW   — Sealed in the shadow-beast Maliketh's blade; stolen in part on the Night of the Black Knives to murder Godwyn the Golden, killing his soul but not his body.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The death that was taken from the world, waiting in a blade to be given back.

